{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>就現場所見，被捕男子黑布蒙頭，雙手被手銬反鎖，警犬奉召到場搜車。</p><p>據了解，警方較早前在上址截查一輛的士，發現的士乘客因無交罰款而遭到通緝。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127034207135076352271058.jpeg/o_dJnOx49fE1UG_IBo0thXheV-lGcFjpx9-urf3frq0\" alt=\"警犬奉召到場搜車。（李家傑攝）\"><figcaption>警犬奉召到場搜車。（李家傑攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127034210880720896460791.jpeg/puygqD-gkJAwy6NnxnrGqPDJuggdmelfTfsbdHf7G3Q\" alt=\"警犬奉召到場搜車。（李家傑攝）\"><figcaption>警犬奉召到場搜車。（李家傑攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127034216807534592403568.jpeg/pLjRd6VwSY4yRZQ3fr-GnYZSYVoe3m20NaJxqg-icao\" alt=\"被捕男子黑布蒙頭，雙手被手銬反鎖。（李家傑攝）\"><figcaption>被捕男子黑布蒙頭，雙手被手銬反鎖。（李家傑攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260501/1127034213724590080459870.jpeg/U_czA5hLxQ1UCKQ3JcpDfb1VCamc-rkHoEa8ZppGvGY\" alt=\"警員檢獲大量毒品。（李家傑攝）\"><figcaption>警員檢獲大量毒品。（李家傑攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T16:23:51.874957+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":141,"images":4,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}